issue.title: 『秒懂本尊答』网上快3计划(网易/知乎）
issue.body: 网上快3计划[秦奋荖師]腾讯Q:3230482│信誉网:f5 666.cc【金牌团队│顶尖计划│导师单带│回血上岸│万人推荐】据腾讯新闻报道助力文化传承和数字科技相结合，腾讯多媒体实验室的引领作用愈发显著。自2022年12月起，腾讯与河南安阳合作，旨在共同推动甲骨文的数字“破译”和传承活化。这次专项合作取得了令人瞩目的阶段性成果，其中腾讯多媒体实验室与SSV数字文化实验室的联手合作，对甲骨文模型数据的压缩与展示取得了重大突破。针对甲骨文3D模型加载速度慢的难题，实验室与合作伙伴共同解决了数据量过大的问题，通过引入快速点云编解码器与渲染引擎，成功实现了数据压缩、传输成本显著降低、展示效果优化的目标。这一突破性进展，不仅让甲骨文文字更加清晰，也大幅减小了数据体积，为甲骨文研究与体验带来全新的视觉体验。注：图片示意用，实际产品可达4K或8K超高清腾讯多媒体实验室的编mpihokplu2024年3月20日1时1分48秒

issue.title: Agent request: create threshold for verified status

labels.name: Priority-Normal (Not urgent)
labels.description: Normal because this needs to get done but not immediately.

milestone.title: Needs Discussion
milestone.description: The path to implementation is unclear and requires discussion by involved parties, the Advisory Committee, and/or the Arctos Group.

issue.body:
Previously brought up but I thought filing an issue will make sure I dont forget it! I would like to propose a minimum set of requirements for an agent to automatically have verified status. At least a minimum threshold so we can request Dusty to do so automatically for all our agents, either a first time pass or set up a script.

For example, agents can be automatically be given the status=verified if they have _any of the following_:

- have at least one identifier (url, github, library of congress or other link)
- have at least one address (correspondence or email)
- have an Arctos operator login
- have at least birth date

thoughts? require more or different? if there seems to be a lot of discussion needed then I will post for the Agent Committee to discuss and recommend-- thx!

comment.body: Some of that is me. I was cataloging and pushing our CA's to verified. I'll go back and change them to accepted.
